author: TIM JONES
title: LIVE: Trump Hosting Town Hall in N.H.
text: Privacy Policy | More Newsletters Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump has returned to the early voting state of New Hampshire. Trump is holding a town hall in Atkinson, where he's discussing what he wants to address in his campaign. Interactive 2016 N.H. Primary Candidate Tracker Among the topics included investing in the country's military. "If I win, we're going to build the strongest military we've had in this country," Trump said. "Nobody is going to mess with us." Trump also took aim at fellow candidates Ben Carson and Jeb Bush, saying Carson was even more low-energy than Bush. He also discusses what he said was the media's portrayal of his campaign, saying it never shows his "massive crowds." Published 2 hours ago
